text.tspan: There are many existing organisations through which you can volunteer. A good way of
volunteering is to help newly arrived to adapt to the society. Stockholm city council are
creating meetings between new and established Swedes. You can volunteer as a tutor,
or just be there as a friend. Its a way to help people in vulnerable situations. This is also
done through a organisation called KompisSverige.
When it comes to the refugee crisis, staying silent is one of the worst things you can do.
is an initiative to spread awareness and knowledge online. Social media
generates discussions among your own communities about the issues refugees are facing.
